<seg id="130">Only a thorough analysis of the construction industries in both countries would have made a final conclusion regarding bridge prices in the Czech Republic and Germany. However, this would have gone beyond the scope of this examination.</seg>
<seg id="131">The border bridge is the most expensive steel composite bridge on the D 8 and A 17.</seg>
