<seg id="860">The new experience and knowledge gained through the cooperation of both auditors form the basis for the successful implementation of future audits in the area of ​​sales tax administration.</seg>
<seg id="861">Communiqué</seg>
<seg id="862">This report has been drawn up in Czech, English and German and signed by the President of the Supreme Control Office of the Czech Republic and the President of the Federal Audit Office of the Federal Republic of Germany.</seg>
